PascalErrorToken

public PascalErrorToken(Source source,
                        PascalErrorCode errorCode,
                        String tokenText)
                 throws Exception
Uses the passed tokenText as text and erorCode as value. The token type is always PascalTokenType.ERROR.

Parameters:
source - The source the token belongs to.
errorCode - Will be the token value.
tokenText - Will be the token text.
Throws:
Exception
